Package: phutil
Title: Persistence Homology Utilities
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Aymeric", "Stamm", , "aymeric.stamm@cnrs.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8725-3654"))
Description: Implements a class for hosting persistence homology information in
    the form of a persistence diagram. The package also provides a set of
    functions to manipulate persistence diagrams, such as coercing them to
    different formats for compatibility with other packages or plotting them.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
